# 🚀 Run Locally

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone <your-repository-url>
```

Open the project folder

```bash
cd portfolio
```

Run a local server

### Python

```bash
python -m http.server 8000
```

### Node.js

```bash
npx serve .
```

Open your browser:

```
http://localhost:8000
```

